{"tid":101350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友成日話我蠢...","createTime":"2017-01-30T17:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T07:36:09.000Z","uid":2870,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b44f414f38e33d34bfb124eba61f5e6a0db4138","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:50:13.000Z","msg":"依幾日又因爲我蠢而鬧交<br />\n事源係佢叫完我做嘅野唔做<br />\n話我明知自己蠢 次次做錯 又唔聽人講野照住做<br />\n<br />\n有時都比佢鬧到好自卑 唔識反應<br />\n覺得自己真係好蠢 咩都唔明 咪唔出聲 比佢鬧<br />\n但又會比佢鬧做咩唔講野 係咪啞咗<br />\n咁我究竟可以點做？<br />\n比人鬧應該咩反應先啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbdde99089c1d43598f4337ca1d1ee71a795a47","tid":101350,"uid":4351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依幾日又因爲我蠢而鬧交<br />\n事源係佢叫完我做嘅野唔做<br />\n話我明知自己蠢 次次做錯 又唔聽人講野照住做<br />\n<br />\n有時都比佢鬧到好自卑 唔識反應<br />\n覺得自己真係好蠢 咩都唔明 咪唔出聲 比佢鬧<br />\n但又會比佢鬧做咩唔講野 係咪啞咗<br />\n咁我究竟可以點做？<br />\n比人鬧應該咩反應先啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講對唔住 跪係到"},{"pid":"cf14edd246a907fd80403f180fa8320c21d5e2bf","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依幾日又因爲我蠢而鬧交<br />\n事源係佢叫完我做嘅野唔做<br />\n話我明知自己蠢 次次做錯 又唔聽人講野照住做<br />\n<br />\n有時都比佢鬧到好自卑 唔識反應<br />\n覺得自己真係好蠢 咩都唔明 咪唔出聲 比佢鬧<br />\n但又會比佢鬧做咩唔講野 係咪啞咗<br />\n咁我究竟可以點做？<br />\n比人鬧應該咩反應先啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講對唔住 跪係到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n傾住電話鬧 講咗對唔住 但又咩用..."},{"pid":"bc9db06af7bbb0e8bac7631772841bc43a7882e9","tid":101350,"uid":29983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依幾日又因爲我蠢而鬧交<br />\n事源係佢叫完我做嘅野唔做<br />\n話我明知自己蠢 次次做錯 又唔聽人講野照住做<br />\n<br />\n有時都比佢鬧到好自卑 唔識反應<br />\n覺得自己真係好蠢 咩都唔明 咪唔出聲 比佢鬧<br />\n但又會比佢鬧做咩唔講野 係咪啞咗<br />\n咁我究竟可以點做？<br />\n比人鬧應該咩反應先啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁錯成點先  試下講詳盡啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3573f23b862ce1f77ea7a0b96fb147afc79d2a","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:08:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依幾日又因爲我蠢而鬧交<br />\n事源係佢叫完我做嘅野唔做<br />\n話我明知自己蠢 次次做錯 又唔聽人講野照住做<br />\n<br />\n有時都比佢鬧到好自卑 唔識反應<br />\n覺得自己真係好蠢 咩都唔明 咪唔出聲 比佢鬧<br />\n但又會比佢鬧做咩唔講野 係咪啞咗<br />\n咁我究竟可以點做？<br />\n比人鬧應該咩反應先啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁錯成點先  試下講詳盡啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢見到個post幾好笑就sd比我睇<br />\n我睇到一半就覺悶 唔覺好笑就無睇到<br />\n就比佢話我做咩唔睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未睇到重點緊係唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話我成日都&quot;以為啱&quot; 唔跟住做<br />\n所以啲野就錯晒<br />\n<br />\n之前都發生過啲&quot;我以為啱&quot;嘅事<br />\n但詳情我唔記得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d054a42919a48f031bac4c32f730c146d045513a","tid":101350,"uid":39717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"我係蠢，但我都叻過架！揀左你做男朋友，叻左呢次就夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f874608bf8ba06a07eefabb71e10b584d58f06","tid":101350,"uid":20882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係蠢，但我都叻過架！揀左你做男朋友，叻左呢次就夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281fa09f47e769332b2b081b2cc62a8e03708180","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係蠢，但我都叻過架！揀左你做男朋友，叻左呢次就夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次試下咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝絲打"},{"pid":"58e8b2af68833b2f2869dc1cae968e067b486f44","tid":101350,"uid":29947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依幾日又因爲我蠢而鬧交<br />\n事源係佢叫完我做嘅野唔做<br />\n話我明知自己蠢 次次做錯 又唔聽人講野照住做<br />\n<br />\n有時都比佢鬧到好自卑 唔識反應<br />\n覺得自己真係好蠢 咩都唔明 咪唔出聲 比佢鬧<br />\n但又會比佢鬧做咩唔講野 係咪啞咗<br />\n咁我究竟可以點做？<br />\n比人鬧應該咩反應先啱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁錯成點先  試下講詳盡啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢見到個post幾好笑就sd比我睇<br />\n我睇到一半就覺悶 唔覺好笑就無睇到<br />\n就比佢話我做咩唔睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未睇到重點緊係唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話我成日都&quot;以為啱&quot; 唔跟住做<br />\n所以啲野就錯晒<br />\n<br />\n之前都發生過啲&quot;我以為啱&quot;嘅事<br />\n但詳情我唔記得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n悶就唔睇好正常姐 咁叫蠢？你男朋友好自我中心下喎 唔跟住做就係蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2dbff7ed22aebf3fac65f02f3029ef07e943c7","tid":101350,"uid":40464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:25:28.000Z","msg":"同我個個一模一樣 大事小事比佢屌到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaaa7adeedb5d2299d3052c211f603d179a88744","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:29:48.000Z","msg":"悶就唔睇好正常姐 咁叫蠢？你男朋友好自我中心下喎 唔跟住做就係蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n可能係我講得唔好<br />\n總之就係好多我認為/以為啱嘅野<br />\n其實係錯嘅 而佢解釋我聽又唔明<br />\n佢形容係 我屌極都唔化 容易黑面 控制唔到情緒<br />\n咁比人鬧 唔通仲笑住咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8738410c8448976f366ae9caf8ea96a8bd3139","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我個個一模一樣 大事小事比佢屌到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知自己蠢 好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣可以拉近距離？"},{"pid":"4a43966166af6e49c35988b7176aaaaa670f3679","tid":101350,"uid":3003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>悶就唔睇好正常姐 咁叫蠢？你男朋友好自我中心下喎 唔跟住做就係蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能係我講得唔好<br />\n總之就係好多我認為/以為啱嘅野<br />\n其實係錯嘅 而佢解釋我聽又唔明<br />\n佢形容係 我屌極都唔化 容易黑面 控制唔到情緒<br />\n咁比人鬧 唔通仲笑住咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n你條仔都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6644ef58f9e5ba88f07de2d6688e86b20f026c0d","tid":101350,"uid":55002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:32:23.000Z","msg":"你男朋友係咪控制狂呀<br />\n你自己都有自己思路嫁<br />\n洗乜下下跟住佢<br />\n如果一味鬧你蠢<br />\n佢應該好少顧你感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea059559213caa5f1923255127cc48f88f009ed","tid":101350,"uid":40464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同我個個一模一樣 大事小事比佢屌到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知自己蠢 好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣可以拉近距離？</blockquote><br />\n最後我發現其實係佢問題多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b943234aa788195fca92beb742e5ec3bb1e335","tid":101350,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:34:43.000Z","msg":"你男朋友諗嘢同小朋友一樣。。。"},{"pid":"c67884efd5d73669cb004c21f7ac40cc0a3b6296","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你男朋友係咪控制狂呀<br />\n你自己都有自己思路嫁<br />\n洗乜下下跟住佢<br />\n如果一味鬧你蠢<br />\n佢應該好少顧你感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢已經無咁控制狂 好咗好多<br />\n其實佢已經成日氹我<br />\n咩都要佢解釋係燥嘅<br />\n<br />\n我知自己衰 唔比佢鬧到喊都唔記得做錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2ded293682833e464ef320834077ba7241c405","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T18:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同我個個一模一樣 大事小事比佢屌到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知自己蠢 好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣可以拉近距離？</blockquote><br />\n最後我發現其實係佢問題多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd71f300d9bf93a0501239cb34debc1fa710faa8","tid":101350,"uid":40464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:14:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同我個個一模一樣 大事小事比佢屌到飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知自己蠢 好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點樣可以拉近距離？</blockquote><br />\n最後我發現其實係佢問題多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連幫佢打paper都可以屌我打得唔好 <br />\n咁你唔自己打?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bbd94a245c5938f581e25fb7d28ef2170545a9a","tid":101350,"uid":16718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:27:49.000Z","msg":"分手吧啦 你們性格唔夾<br />\n搵個鐘意你蠢，包容到你蠢的人<br />\n否則佢會嫌你蠢，佢炆，你又覺得委屈、唔開心"},{"pid":"7863334d983139ca00157e34d19c47f67e087a52","tid":101350,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:47:27.000Z","msg":"我以前女朋友讀書好好<br />\n我就相反 讀書一般般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢搏咀唔夠我叻 <br />\n其實冇話蠢唔蠢 要互補不足 <br />\n人冇十全十美嘅 要識得搵長處"},{"pid":"8e8edf96163a811baad079b45912a825fbea8f07","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T01:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n最後我發現其實係佢問題多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連幫佢打paper都可以屌我打得唔好 <br />\n咁你唔自己打?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫佢打埋都比佢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n絲打仲同佢一齊緊？"},{"pid":"bdcae60a693684f2ed4168e863d984636190ddea","tid":101350,"uid":38464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T01:36:27.000Z","msg":"樓主係m﹐大家可以收工"},{"pid":"261d711c995f3752413e1435855aad8055093e64","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T01:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前女朋友讀書好好<br />\n我就相反 讀書一般般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係佢搏咀唔夠我叻 <br />\n其實冇話蠢唔蠢 要互補不足 <br />\n人冇十全十美嘅 要識得搵長處</blockquote><br />\n同你有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我讀書唔係話好好 純粹考得高分過男朋友少少<br />\n係個啲死讀爛讀嘅人 佢就轉數快 識嘅野多<br />\n同佢鬧交永遠都駁唔到 即使我覺得係歪理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除咗成日話我蠢 已經覺得佢好好 只係因為咁唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d625e29452c3616ee586b5f15be2c565f21a9b","tid":101350,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T01:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係m﹐大家可以收工</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}